1
00:00:00,753 --> 00:00:06,653
I bought two expensive dictionaries here half an hour ago,
半小时前我在这里买了两本很贵的辞典,

2
00:00:07,314 --> 00:00:11,484
but I forgot to take them with me.
但是我忘了带走他们.

3
00:00:12,737 --> 00:00:15,085
Who served you, sir?
是谁服务您的,先生?

4
00:00:15,501 --> 00:00:19,448
The lady who is standing behind the counter.
站在柜台后面的那位女士.

5
00:00:19,449 --> 00:00:22,063
Which books did you buy?
您买的是两本什么书?

6
00:00:22,936 --> 00:00:26,217
The books which are on the counter.
就是柜台上的那两本.

7
00:00:26,804 --> 00:00:32,001
Did you serve this gentleman half an hour ago, Caroline?
Caroline,半小时前你服务过这位先生吗?

8
00:00:32,494 --> 00:00:37,107
He says he's the man who bought these books.
他说他就是买这两本书的人.

9
00:00:37,108 --> 00:00:40,044
I can't remember.
我记不起来了.

10
00:00:40,389 --> 00:00:45,276
The man who I served was wearing a hat.
我服务的那个人戴着一顶帽子.

11
00:00:45,477 --> 00:00:50,875
Have you got a hat, sir? Yes, I have.
先生,您有帽子吗?有的,我有帽子.

12
00:00:51,314 --> 00:00:54,019
Would you put it on, please? 
请您把帽子戴上好吗?

13
00:00:54,020 --> 00:00:55,682
All right.
好吧.

14
00:00:56,287 --> 00:01:00,431
Is this the man that you served, Caroline?
Caroline,这就是你接服务的那个人吗?

15
00:01:00,780 --> 00:01:05,164
Yes.I recognize him now.
是他.我现在认出他来了.

